23things_learnmore_small People have very diverse needs in terms of what data literacy means for them.

Choose one or two from the list below and explore “data literacy” from the perspectives of these diverse roles:

    Librarians: What is Data Literacy? (Links to an external site.)Links to an external site. (from databrarians.org)
    Entrepreneurs: Data Literacy -- What It Is And Why None of Us Have It (Links to an external site.)Links to an external site. (from Forbes Magazine)
